      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you about the doctor but i really just want to know if there is a way to do it safely. if i was going to do this, like if i took like 1000mg of garlic extract every day and replaced my lunch with a big spinach smoothie, would that be enough to keep my blood thin? i'm just looking for some numbers or a starting point so i don't do something stupid.",
